{"text_id":119764,"tokens":["Colon"," cancer"," is"," a"," serious"," and"," potentially"," deadly"," disease"," that"," often"," goes"," undetected"," until"," it"," is"," too"," late","."," However",","," there"," are"," steps"," you"," can"," take"," to"," screen"," for"," colon"," cancer"," and"," detect"," it"," early",","," making"," it"," easier"," to"," treat","."," In"," this"," article",","," we"," will"," discuss"," five"," different"," methods"," for"," screening"," for"," colon"," cancer",","," including"," genetic"," testing",","," speaking"," to"," your"," doctor"," if"," you"," have"," inflammatory"," bowel"," disease"," (","IB","D","),"," being"," aware"," of"," other"," risk"," factors",","," reporting"," suspicious"," symptoms",","," and"," undergoing"," tumor"," marker"," testing"," if"," you"," have"," had"," colon"," cancer"," in"," the"," past",".","\n\n","Method"," ","1",":"," Receive"," earlier"," and"," more"," frequent"," screening"," if"," you"," have"," an"," increased"," genetic"," risk",".","\n\n","The"," interesting"," thing"," about"," colon"," cancer"," is"," that"," most"," cases"," are"," not"," related"," to"," genetics","."," However",","," if"," you"," have"," a"," family"," history"," of"," colon"," cancer"," or"," have"," been"," diagnosed"," with"," specific"," genetic"," conditions",","," such"," as"," Lynch"," syndrome"," or"," familial"," aden","omatous"," poly","posis"," (","F","AP","),"," you"," may"," have"," a"," higher"," risk"," of"," developing"," colon"," cancer","."," If"," this"," is"," the"," case",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," speak"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," earlier"," and"," more"," frequent"," colon"," cancer"," screenings",".","\n\n","Method"," ","2",":"," Speak"," to"," your"," doctor"," if"," you"," have"," Crohn","'","s"," disease"," or"," ulcer","ative"," colitis",".","\n\n","Both"," Chron","'","s"," disease"," and"," ulcer","ative"," colitis"," are"," forms"," of"," IBD"," that"," can"," increase"," your"," risk"," of"," developing"," colon"," cancer","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," speak"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," screening"," for"," colon"," cancer"," if"," you"," have"," either"," of"," these"," conditions",".","\n\n","Method"," ","3",":"," Be"," aware"," of"," other"," risk"," factors"," for"," colon"," cancer",".","\n\n","People"," who"," are"," overweight"," or"," obese",","," who"," live"," a"," sedentary"," lifestyle",","," who"," consume"," lots"," of"," red"," meat"," or"," processed"," meats",","," who"," smoke",","," or"," who"," consume"," a"," large"," amount"," of"," alcohol"," are"," all"," at"," an"," increased"," risk"," of"," colon"," cancer","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," be"," aware"," of"," these"," risk"," factors"," and"," take"," steps"," to"," reduce"," your"," risk",","," such"," as"," maintaining"," a"," healthy"," weight",","," exercising"," regularly",","," and"," avoiding"," smoking"," and"," excessive"," alcohol"," consumption",".","\n\n","Method"," ","4",":"," Report"," any"," suspicious"," symptoms"," to"," your"," doctor"," immediately",".","\n\n","If"," you"," notice"," signs"," or"," symptoms"," that"," may"," be"," indicative"," of"," colon"," cancer",","," such"," as"," blood"," in"," your"," stools",","," changes"," in"," bowel"," habits",","," unexplained"," weight"," loss",","," or"," abdominal"," pain",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," report"," them"," to"," your"," doctor"," immediately","."," Early"," detection"," can"," significantly"," improve"," your"," chances"," of"," successful"," treatment",".","\n\n","Method"," ","5",":"," Be"," screened"," with"," tumor"," markers"," if"," you"," have"," had"," colon"," cancer"," in"," the"," past",".","\n\n","If"," you"," have"," previously"," had"," colon"," cancer",","," you"," can"," have"," a"," tumor"," marker"," called"," \"","CEA","\""," measured"," via"," a"," blood"," test"," and"," monitored"," in"," set"," intervals"," following"," your"," treatment"," for"," the"," cancer","."," This"," can"," help"," detect"," any"," potential"," recur","rences"," of"," the"," cancer"," early"," on",","," making"," it"," easier"," to"," treat",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," screening"," for"," colon"," cancer"," is"," crucial"," for"," early"," detection"," and"," treatment","."," By"," following"," the"," steps"," outlined"," in"," this"," article",","," you"," can"," reduce"," your"," risk"," of"," developing"," colon"," cancer"," and"," improve"," your"," chances"," of"," successful"," treatment"," if"," you"," are"," diagnosed","."," If"," you"," have"," any"," concerns"," or"," questions"," about"," colon"," cancer"," screening",","," be"," sure"," to"," speak"," to"," your"," doctor","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}